                     <interp inst="t17770910-63-off307" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a silk handkerchief, value 3 s. half a guinea, and half a crown
            </rs>, the property of 
               <persName id="t17770910-63-victim516" type="victimName">
                  James
                   Pearce
               <interp inst="t17770910-63-victim516" type="surname" value="Pearce"></interp>
